<br>
Your posts and comments stated that bards were 'worthless' and that you no longer enjoyed them.  We merely stated that they weren't worthless.  This was before:<br>
<br>
1)  Chains nerf was declared &quot;as designed&quot; after having been told it would be fixed.<br>
2)  Mez was declared &quot;as designed&quot; with a 70% resist rate<br>
3)  Haste bug was fixed, effectively reducing the power of bardic haste songs to near worthlessness in any multi-group raid that contained an enchanter.  Formerly a group with an enchanter (and using haste items) could have the bard do hastes and be just as effective, freeing the enchanter to do other things, this is no longer true because they fixed this bug.  A group without an enchanter could be very effective with a bard if they had haste items as well.  The bug fix is <!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> not</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--> a bad thing, just one more thing which makes bards less effective than they once were.<br>
<br>
All 3 of these things have become true after your initial complaints about the class.  You can't sit there saying &quot;I told you so&quot; when most of us were already unhappy but sitting it out hoping that the issues above would be fixed, or addressed, in a way not to harm bards viability as a class in the upper levels.<br>
<br>
Bottom line:  Yes, when you posted bards weren't &quot;as good&quot; as they had been pre-50 but, now, after the latest series of announcments and patches by Verant bards are even LESS effective thus causing many who were near, or on, the fence to jump over and decide that it's no longer worth the frustration of being a bard in the post-50 levels.  I still think bard is the best class, hands down, pre-50.<br>
<br>
So, no you didn't &quot;Tell me so&quot; you merely predicted, correctly, what would happen.  I'm sorry you were right, but you were.  As Kaluian said, many of us had our frustrations with the class long before you ever posted but kept it to ourselves or our guildmates longer than you, that's all <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <br>
<br>
**shrugs**<br>
If you want to be petty that's fine.  Make mine apple please.<br>
<br>
